johar.interfaceinterpreter.star
Class IdfAnalyzer

java.lang.Object
  johar.interfaceinterpreter.star.IdfAnalyzer

public class IdfAnalyzer
extends java.lang.Object

Provides access to various information about the specified IDF (e.g list of queryable/non-queryable params in a command/stage, list of questions in a command, list of tables, list of browsable tables, etc.).
